    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款紧张刺激的店铺经营游戏中，感受狩猎、屠宰和烹饪的快感。狩猎可爱的怪物，然后大卸八块，尽量以最快的速度煮给顾客食用。总之一句话：想让店铺生存下去，就得快准狠！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231430/extras/f5b40b3290780effb303f751957e096c.avif?t=1770065984\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231430/extras_big/f5b40b3290780effb303f751957e096c.avif?t=1770065984 width=800 height=375 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >屠宰 - 解剖巨大的怪物尸体，卖肉赚钱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231430/extras/479f9bd2a05956458c04f858632fd71b.avif?t=1770065984\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231430/extras_big/479f9bd2a05956458c04f858632fd71b.avif?t=1770065984 width=800 height=375 /></span>烹饪 - 为每名顾客烹制想要的美食，也可以制作并销售大众喜爱的食品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231430/extras/bae82c3bb39be9aa3b1ab9ab2f3bfa01.avif?t=1770065984\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231430/extras_big/bae82c3bb39be9aa3b1ab9ab2f3bfa01.avif?t=1770065984 width=800 height=375 /></span>战斗 - 劈、剁、砍，把敌人切成美味的肉块。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231430/extras/2644044f49ed6c86a5190bea719e698d.avif?t=1770065984\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231430/extras_big/2644044f49ed6c86a5190bea719e698d.avif?t=1770065984 width=800 height=375 /></span>销售 - 顾客络绎不绝。给他们想要的食物，他们就不会生气。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
